The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-28-2013 WED






The Glenn Beck Program - 08/28/13 


The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET



Today, Glenn talks about a special plaque and a sweet letter he received.

 Also, Glenn looks at how Syria could affect your life.
 Plus, Glenn discusses how a new movement could rise up in congress


 and the first week of ratings for Al Jazeera are in.
